  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nI cannot find how to use  [forge-script options](https://book.getfoundry.sh/reference/forge/forge-script?highlight=Solidity%20Scripting#options) and [Solidity Scripting](https://book.getfoundry.sh/tutorials/solidity-scripting) to handle maxPriorityFeePerGas or maxFeePerGas (eip-1559).\r\n\r\nI made a [similar issue](https://github.com/NomicFoundation/hardhat/issues/3298) & [pr](https://github.com/NomicFoundation/hardhat/pull/3331) on hardhat. \r\n\r\nfor better gas optimization for dev, I think forge-scripting with eip-1559 adopt is quite important feature.\n\n### Additional context\n\nI attached some links above. ",
